{"tid":777360,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《鐵馬尋橋》兄弟班包圍唐詩詠 未行禮已玩到癲","createTime":"2018-08-12T23:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T09:12:44.000Z","uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"61c828764b54b495f80898e18263eec4c4d94ee9","tid":777360,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T23:37:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2018/08/12/3673638/20180812_ent_907_mp4_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F3673638%2F20180812_ent_907_mp4_w.mp4&d=%2B5Q0IrOHhkUFI4%2F8znlASL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=583e4dc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2018/08/12/3673638/20180812_ent_907_mp4_w.mp4</a><br />\n <br />\n鄭嘉穎、陳凱琳今日結婚，一對準新人暫時仲未現身，不過一班圈中好友就紛紛喺社交網分享照片或視頻，黃智賢剛喺instagram分享咗短片，留言：「七星伴月，恭喜一對新人。」<br />\n<br />\n點解係「七星伴月」?因為有七個男人圍住唐詩詠囉！呢七條仔包括有黃智賢、唐文龍、黎耀祥、黃嘉樂、曹永廉、林子善同馬國明，着住花裙嘅詩詠企係一堆男人中間。大家心情都好興奮，仲一齊對住詩詠做咗個伸出魔爪嘅動作，曹永廉仲講笑話：「好似想鍊死佢咁。」詩詠俾呢班《鐵馬尋橋》好兄弟，搞到大笑，兼笑到失晒儀態。而陳嘉寶(Anjaylia)同賴慰玲亦都扮到靚靚出席婚禮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180812/large/1534062460_e6c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180812%2Flarge%2F1534062460_e6c6.jpg&h=6cac56b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 七個男人圍住唐詩詠(黃智賢IG影片截圖) <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180812/large/1534062460_6c80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180812%2Flarge%2F1534062460_6c80.jpg&h=e4a576b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 着住花裙嘅詩詠企係一堆男人中間(黃智賢IG影片截圖) <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180812/large/1534062456_b9f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180812%2Flarge%2F1534062456_b9f3.jpg&h=6a6fa990&s={SIZE}\" /><br 